{"tid":822634,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"中大宣布明日停工停課","createTime":"2018-09-16T12:12:47.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-16T12:22:30.000Z","uid":164435,"like":7,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"a2af5ddb936885a3a58440bf981a7039713d9f2b","tid":822634,"uid":164435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-16T12:12:47.000Z","msg":"【Now新聞台】香港中文大學表示，受強颱風山竹的影響，校園內有樹木倒塌，校內多條主要道路受阻。為確保學生和教職員的安全，以及考慮到清理工作需時，大學宣布明日停課一日。除有需要處理職務的員工可在安全的情況下回校履行職務外，大學其他員工均毋須回校。大學呼籲所有學生和教職員留意天氣情況，注意安全。"},{"pid":"1df43c9fab9a2db5fd34bebfcb451ab1856e1e49","tid":822634,"uid":164435,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-16T12:14:52.000Z","msg":"科大 <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/822477/\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/822477/</a><br />\n浸大 <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/822624/\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/822624/</a>"},{"pid":"2d8b5101eddaa706d2f9e33a861618b600581402","tid":822634,"uid":45914,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-16T12:16:50.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"efdf60b834739063d83e087bf735460f018fca32","tid":822634,"uid":30966,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"2d8b5101eddaa706d2f9e33a861618b600581402","tid":822634,"uid":45914,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-16T12:16:50.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-16T12:17:47.000Z","msg":"ust咪話放囉"},{"pid":"eb4e3a5bc34be71f8cb9fbe4fa87d1382bce17d0","tid":822634,"uid":164435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-16T12:21:12.000Z","msg":"停課 : 科大、中大、浸大、教大"},{"pid":"5da0a368c260ff2069dc21b8d4a3b74b8edf3541","tid":822634,"uid":123920,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"eb4e3a5bc34be71f8cb9fbe4fa87d1382bce17d0","tid":822634,"uid":164435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-16T12:21:12.000Z","msg":"停課 : 科大、中大、浸大、教大"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-16T12:22:17.000Z","msg":"仲有poly"}